					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="How to Define and Implement a Social Mission for Your Business" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20150221080156-shutterstock-116923705.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
